      <h2>My Story</h2>
      <p>My coding journey began in college when I started learning C++. Although there was no hands-on output through a computer, I was determined to learn programming. I read books like "Python 2nd Edition" and utilized free resources to expand my knowledge.</p>
      <p>To further my learning, I created a roadmap that included HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It was during this time that I discovered Holberton School's website, which has been instrumental in helping me develop this website.</p>
      <p>Through persistence, self-motivation, and continuous learning, I have been able to overcome obstacles and make progress in my coding journey.</p>
      <p>Remember:</p>
